## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-102">声明是有关由颁发者的使用者的声明。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-102">A claim is a statement about a subject by an issuer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-103">声明表示的使用者在身份验证和授权操作的上下文中有用的属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-103">Claims represent attributes of the subject that are useful in the context of authentication and authorization operations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-104">使用者和颁发者是属于身份方案这两个实体。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-104">Subjects and issuers are both entities that are part of an identity scenario.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-105">使用者的一些典型示例包括： 用户、 应用程序或服务、 设备或计算机。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-105">Some typical examples of a subject are: a user, an application or service, a device, or a computer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-106">颁发者的一些典型示例包括： 操作系统、 应用程序。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-106">Some typical examples of an issuer are: the operating system, an application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-107">服务、 角色提供程序、 标识提供程序，或联合身份验证提供程序中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-107">a service, a role provider, an identity provider, or a federation provider.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-108">颁发者通过颁发安全令牌，通常通过安全令牌服务 (STS) 来提供声明。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-108">An issuer delivers claims by issuing security tokens, typically through a Security Token Service (STS).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-109">(在 WIF，可以通过从派生生成 STS<xref:System.IdentityModel.SecurityTokenService>类。)有时，通过存储直接在该资源的使用者属性可以扩展从颁发者收到的声明的集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-109">(In WIF, you can build an STS by deriving from the <xref:System.IdentityModel.SecurityTokenService> class.) On occasion, the collection of claims received from an issuer can be extended by subject attributes stored directly at the resource.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-110">声明可进行计算以确定对数据的访问权限和其他保护在授权的过程中的资源，并且也可以使用来使或 express 关于某主题的身份验证决策。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-110">A claim can be evaluated to determine access rights to data and other secured resources during the process of authorization and can also be used to make or express authentication decisions about a subject.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-111">从.NET 4.5 开始，Windows Identity Foundation (WIF) 类，该类实现基于声明的标识，已完全集成到.NET Framework。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-111">Beginning with .NET 4.5, the Windows Identity Foundation (WIF) classes, which implement claims-based identity, have been fully integrated into the .NET Framework.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-112">声明概念由实现<xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim>类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-112">The claims concept is implemented by the <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim> class.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-113">下面介绍的重要属性<xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim>类：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-113">The following describes important properties of the <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim> class:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-114"><xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Type%2A>属性是一个字符串 (通常是一个 URI) 包含有关声明的语义信息; 它告诉你声明的值的含义。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-114">The <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Type%2A> property is a string (typically a URI) that contains the semantic information about the claim; it tells you what the value of the claim means.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-115">例如，具有声明类型的声明<xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimTypes.GivenName>("http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/ws/2005/05/identity/claims/givenname") 表示用户的名字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-115">For example, a claim with a claim type of <xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimTypes.GivenName> ("http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/ws/2005/05/identity/claims/givenname") represents a user’s first name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-116">值<xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Type%2A>属性可以是定义中的已知声明类型之一<xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimTypes>类，也可以是任意一个 URI，定义由颁发者。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-116">The value of the <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Type%2A> property can be one of the well-known claim types defined in the <xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimTypes> class, or it can be an arbitrary URI as defined by the issuer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-117">例如，一个声明类型为"urn: spendinglimit"可能表示一个用户特性，颁发者的业务上下文中有意义。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-117">For example, a claim type of "urn:spendinglimit" might represent a user attribute which makes sense within the business context of the issuer.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-118"><xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Value%2A>属性包含声明的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-118">The <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Value%2A> property contains the value of the claim.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-119">为了减少依赖关系并简化管理，可在 WIF 声明的值被表示仅为字符串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-119">In order to reduce dependencies and simplify administration, in WIF the value of a claim is represented only as a string.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-120">对于更复杂的值类型，建议你使用标准的 XML 架构类型来表示的值是用于将序列化到并从字符串反序列化方式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-120">For more complex value types, it is recommended that you use standard XML schema types to indicate how the value is meant to be serialized into and deserialized from a string.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-121"><xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.ValueType%2A>属性包含标识值的类型信息的字符串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-121">The <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.ValueType%2A> property contains a string that identifies the type information for the value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-122">应使用此属性，以了解值的格式并提供有关如何反序列化信息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-122">This property should be used to understand the format of the value and to provide information about how to deserialize it.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-123">如果你的解决方案需要复杂的值类型，建议你使用中的标准 XML 架构类型<xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.ValueType%2A>属性以指示如何<xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Value%2A>属性是用于将序列化到和从字符串反序列化。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-123">If your solution requires complex value types, it is recommended that you use standard XML schema types in the <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.ValueType%2A> property to indicate how the <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Value%2A> property is meant to be serialized into and deserialized from a string.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-124"><xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Subject%2A>属性是<xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimsIdentity>表示声明主题的对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-124">The <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Subject%2A> property is a <xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimsIdentity> object that represents the subject of the claim.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-125">声明的使用者是有关断言声明的实体 （通常请求资源的访问权限的用户）。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-125">The subject of the claim is the entity (typically the user who is requesting access to a resource) about which the claim is asserted.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-126"><xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimsIdentity>包含，在其属性之间的描述的属性的声明的集合和属性的使用者，因为一个或多个颁发者通过证明。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-126">The <xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimsIdentity> contains, among its properties, a collection of claims that describe the properties and attributes of the subject as attested to by one or more issuers.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-127"><xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Issuer%2A>属性包含颁发声明的实体的名称。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-127">The <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Issuer%2A> property contains the name of the entity that issued the claim.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-128">声明的颁发者是在由 WIF 包含由颁发者名称注册表维护的已知的颁发者列表中获取的名称的字符串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-128">The issuer of a claim is represented in WIF by a string that contains a name taken from a list of well-known issuers that is maintained by the issuer name registry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-129">颁发者名称注册表是派生自的类的实例<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.IssuerNameRegistry>类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-129">The issuer name registry is an instance of a class that derives from the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.IssuerNameRegistry> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-130">颁发者名称注册表将验证由相应的颁发者的令牌的签名所需的加密材料的助记键名称相关联。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-130">The issuer name registry associates a mnemonic name to the cryptographic material needed to verify the signatures of tokens produced by the corresponding issuer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-131">例如，<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.ConfigurationBasedIssuerNameRegistry>类，可在初始状态下.NET 4.5 起，将每个颁发者的助记键名称与及其相应的 X.509 证书相关联。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-131">For example, the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.ConfigurationBasedIssuerNameRegistry> class, available out of the box with .NET 4.5, associates the mnemonic name for each issuer with its corresponding X.509 certificate.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-132">通常，由颁发者名称注册表在启动时对已知颁发者的列表是生成。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-132">The list of well-known issuers is typically built at startup time by the issuer name registry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-133">使用的列表<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.ConfigurationBasedIssuerNameRegistry>在应用程序配置文件中指定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-133">The list used by the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.ConfigurationBasedIssuerNameRegistry> is specified in the application configuration file.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-134"><xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.OriginalIssuer%2A>属性包含最初发出声明的实体的名称。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-134">The <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.OriginalIssuer%2A> property contains the name of the entity that originally issued the claim.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-135">此属性旨在促进其中声明之前可能需要等待多个颁发者通过它提供的到 RP 应用程序，客户端的方案例如联合身份验证方案。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-135">This property is designed to facilitate scenarios where a claim may pass through multiple issuers before it is presented by the client to the RP application; such as federation scenarios.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-136">你可以检查<xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.OriginalIssuer%2A>属性来确定最初发出声明的实体。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-136">You can examine the <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.OriginalIssuer%2A> property to determine the entity that originally issued the claim.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-137">该名称被从列表中的已知颁发者颁发者名称注册表中，如下所示的情况下由维护<xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Issuer%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-137">The name is taken from the list of well-known issuers maintained by the issuer name registry, as in the case of the <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Issuer%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-138">下面的示例提取到执行 HTTP 请求的经过身份验证用户关联的声明，并将其写入 HTTP 响应中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-138">The following example extracts the claims associated to the authenticated user performing an HTTP request and writes them in the HTTP response.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-139">当前用户读取从<xref:System.Web.HttpContext>作为<xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimsPrincipal>和从其读取声明。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-139">The current user is read from the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> as a <xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimsPrincipal> and the claims are read from it.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6ab7-140">声明然后写入到<xref:System.Web.HttpResponse>对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6ab7-140">The claims are then written to the <xref:System.Web.HttpResponse> object.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
ClaimsPrincipal principal = HttpContext.Current.User as ClaimsPrincipal;  
if (null != principal)  
{  
   foreach (Claim claim in principal.Claims)  
   {  
      Response.Write("CLAIM TYPE: " + claim.Type + "; CLAIM VALUE: " + claim.Value + "</br>");  
   }  
  
}  
  
```
